        rhizoids buried in soil. Perichaetial leaves highly differentiated, closely sheathing, apex
        obtuse to rounded and laminal cells mostly rhomboid and smooth throughout.</description>
    <phenology>Capsules mature spring–summer (Mar–Aug, Jun).</phenology>
